metadata.name: GHNFT ARMY
metadata.description:
United as one -

We must pledge together as a community to create an unbreakable Army unphased by FUD. With a mission to destroy and publicly shame all paperhands.

We must pledge to always honor and commit to our project founder, expressed always by having full faith & trust in our leader.

To pledge our belief in the entire process, never to crack under pressure as for pressure is our greatest resource to building the foundation of our Diamondhands Army, through pressure, commitment, and unity we shall prevail.

The mission doesn't end at 69 ETH... it's just the beginning!

Stay Strong my Comrades
